message: Let's get this started, I'm willing to give you a good deal, but don't expect me to go easy on you!
You're starting strong, but I'm not afraid to take the lead!
You think you can take the lead? Let's see how long you can keep it up!
You're trying to cut me down, but I'm not going to back down!
You're not backing down, I respect that. But I'm not going to give up either!
I'm not backing down, and I'm not going to let you take the lead!
You're not going to take the lead that easily, I've got a good feeling about this!
I'm not getting tired, I'm just getting started!
You're getting close to exhaustion, but I'm just getting started!
You think you're getting the upper hand, but I'm not going down without a fight!
You're getting close to breaking a sweat, I can feel it!
You're trying to wear me down, but I'm not going to crack!
You're not going to take the lead, I'm going to take control!
You're trying to take control, but I'm still in the driver's seat!
I'm not giving up yet! I'll take one last shot at getting a good deal!
It's now or never, Alice. Take it or leave it!
